WEBVTT

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.940
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:28.320
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.070
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:42.180
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.990
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.060
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.720
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:56.760 --> 00:00:59.940
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:03.220
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.890
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.920
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.280
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:22.360
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:26.020
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.350
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:33.790
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:35.040
=The Lead=

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.789
=Episode 48=

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:39.439
Qin'e.

00:01:41.599 --> 00:01:45.279
I've always felt I've been
an incompetent troupe leader,

00:01:47.039 --> 00:01:49.599
just barely holding
this troupe together.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:52.120
But seeing this paper of yours today,

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:55.800
I finally feel like
I can stand tall for once.

00:01:58.079 --> 00:01:58.839
Troupe Leader.

00:02:01.359 --> 00:02:02.320
For these years,

00:02:03.359 --> 00:02:04.480
thank you.

00:02:05.199 --> 00:02:05.839
You're welcome.

00:02:05.839 --> 00:02:07.760
I'm the troupe leader. It's my duty.

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:12.520
You can leave now.

00:02:13.119 --> 00:02:14.679
L-Let me calm down a bit.

00:02:23.679 --> 00:02:24.399
Qin'e.

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:27.880
Do not tell anyone.

00:02:27.880 --> 00:02:29.039
It's embarrassing.

00:02:29.600 --> 00:02:30.439
Got it.

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:38.679
Since Yi Qin'e's comeback
is on the agenda,

00:02:38.679 --> 00:02:39.719
then my new play...

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:42.319
Let's not mention
your unfinished script.

00:02:43.359 --> 00:02:45.040
Give me half a month,
and I'll finish it.

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:49.760
I believe the most urgent issue now

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:52.959
is addressing the loss
of Qinqiang opera audiences.

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:55.040
Nowadays,

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:59.159
the people's growing cultural
and spiritual needs

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:03.159
and the scarce performance market
have formed a sharp contradiction.

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:04.599
Stop that talk.

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:06.519
Make it plain.

00:03:07.079 --> 00:03:08.239
How about classic operas?

00:03:08.359 --> 00:03:09.040
The popular ones.

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:12.239
How about Bai She Zhuan?

00:03:12.239 --> 00:03:13.519
I could still play Xu Xian.

00:03:13.719 --> 00:03:15.439
Didn't you switch to the Laodan role?

00:03:15.439 --> 00:03:16.719
Mr. Qin, hey you.

00:03:16.719 --> 00:03:18.040
I can play She Taijun

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:19.239
in Yang Men Nyu Jiang.

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:22.159
Then I think Hu Xian Jie is better.

00:03:22.159 --> 00:03:24.079
Qin'e went through
her own ordeal, didn't she?

00:03:24.959 --> 00:03:26.480
Why not the new play I'm working on?

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:28.040
I can finish it in seven days.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.799
Perform You Xi Hu.

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:39.239
Let's finish that opera
we couldn't five years ago.

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:49.080
Here, let me do it.

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:52.360
Mom, what else would you like?

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:53.520
Order two more cold dishes.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:54.080
No need.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:55.439
Order whatever you'd like.

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:56.719
Okay, I'll do it.

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:06.680
I'll go to the restroom.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:07.840
I'll go with you.

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:09.080
It's fine, Mom. I'll go alone.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:10.039
Let me accompany you.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:11.879
You stay here with Mom.

00:04:12.479 --> 00:04:13.360
I'll go by myself.

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:15.879
Be careful then.

00:04:15.879 --> 00:04:16.719
Okay.

00:04:25.560 --> 00:04:27.520
Mom, thank you.

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:28.840
What?

00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:30.479
Thank you for this new home.

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:31.800
Rest assured.

00:04:31.800 --> 00:04:33.400
Once I save up the eighty thousand yuan,

00:04:33.400 --> 00:04:34.360
I'll repay you.

00:04:34.919 --> 00:04:36.240
Don't mind that.

00:04:38.879 --> 00:04:39.919
One more thing.

00:04:39.919 --> 00:04:42.479
Ning's mother is worried about Ning,
so she wants to come

00:04:42.479 --> 00:04:44.159
and take care of her.

00:04:44.159 --> 00:04:44.879
What do you think?

00:04:44.879 --> 00:04:45.639
It's only right.

00:04:45.824 --> 00:04:46.800
Her daughter has a baby,

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:48.800
as her mother, she must be worried.

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:49.719
When is she coming?

00:04:50.439 --> 00:04:51.599
She arrives tomorrow.

00:04:51.599 --> 00:04:52.680
You should pick her up.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:04:59.879
Well, Mom.

00:04:59.879 --> 00:05:01.800
The new home only has two rooms.

00:05:02.479 --> 00:05:05.400
Maybe I'll get you a room
at the hotel downstairs.

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:18.039
Actually, you could go to Uncle Sanyuan.

00:05:18.439 --> 00:05:20.840
You two delayed things
for years because of me.

00:05:20.840 --> 00:05:22.759
Now is the perfect time.

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:24.639
What do you mean?

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:27.520
I have been tough my whole life.

00:05:27.520 --> 00:05:28.520
At this age,

00:05:29.599 --> 00:05:31.240
what I do or where I go

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:32.199
isn't for you to decide.

00:06:48.639 --> 00:06:49.439
Why are you here?

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.120
Dropping off something.

00:06:51.879 --> 00:06:53.360
I moved out from Zhang Hao's place.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.160
It's not safe
to leave all this in the hotel.

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:57.079
You keep them for me.

00:06:57.079 --> 00:06:58.759
I'll get them once I find a new place.

00:06:59.040 --> 00:06:59.720
I'm leaving now.

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:00.819
Stop!

00:07:04.839 --> 00:07:06.199
Wait, what are you doing?

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:08.079
What's wrong with you?

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:09.000
What's wrong?

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:12.199
Wait, what do you mean?

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.240
W-What am I to you?

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:17.279
Why can't you trust me?

00:07:18.120 --> 00:07:20.879
Can't you count on me
when you're in trouble?

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:23.480
Give me a chance. You can count on me.

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:29.360
You always handle everything alone.

00:07:29.360 --> 00:07:31.800
Looking for a new place?
This is a place to live.

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:33.079
Can't you stay here?

00:07:34.600 --> 00:07:36.600
We've been hesitating most of our lives.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.920
What are you doing? What's the point?

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:43.600
What's wrong?

00:07:44.519 --> 00:07:46.600
Turn around and go inside. Get inside.

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:51.199
Get inside.

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.199
It's locked.

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:04.480
You ruined such a romantic moment.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:07.279
Is it this key?

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:12.420
That's it.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:13.620
Thank you.

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:14.959
You're welcome.

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:16.060
How is it?

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:18.800
Why did you refit it?

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:20.639
You said you had attachment to it.

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:22.920
I can't throw it away or sell it.

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:24.320
So I installed electric wheels.

00:08:24.399 --> 00:08:25.759
It can run really fast.

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:29.160
Hop on and try it. Come on.

00:08:33.040 --> 00:08:34.360
It's really spacious.

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:36.720
Now that it's electric,
it runs faster, right?

00:08:37.759 --> 00:08:40.959
No matter how fast it runs,
it can't keep up with the times.

00:08:41.639 --> 00:08:44.160
No matter how fast it runs,
it can't outrun the changes.

00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:46.160
Have you decided what you'll do?

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:48.240
I want to sing opera.

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.240
I've been waiting for this.

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:51.879
Let's go. Let's head out.

00:08:51.879 --> 00:08:52.759
Where are we going?

00:08:54.519 --> 00:08:56.040
To take care of an important event.

00:08:58.680 --> 00:09:02.800
(Putting on a grand opera
is actually about control.)

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:04.040
(Where to be gentle,)

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:05.279
(and where to be thrilled.)

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:09.600
(Steadiness is the foundation
for a protagonist.)

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:14.800
(From the moment one steps on stage,
one must have the bearing of a general.)

00:09:15.079 --> 00:09:18.319
(The bearing of a general
isn't just on the surface,)

00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:23.160
(but confidence and composure
from the inside.)

00:09:23.800 --> 00:09:25.560
(Half a life has passed,)

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:29.720
(only now has Yi Qin'e begun
to understand the meaning of this.)

00:09:29.759 --> 00:09:31.519
Is the training a bit too tough?

00:09:32.439 --> 00:09:34.040
After all, she's not young anymore.

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:39.399
A woman must be tough on herself.

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:55.120
We're here.

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:57.160
Be careful.

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:59.000
Why does it look different?

00:10:00.839 --> 00:10:02.399
Many years have passed.

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:17.960
Lower your head.

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:21.519
Okay, three, two, one.

00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:24.159
(Ningzhou County Marriage Registration)
What are they doing?

00:10:25.159 --> 00:10:26.559
This isn't even a holiday.

00:10:26.879 --> 00:10:28.200
Why are they taking a break?

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:30.639
They said there's a power outage,

00:10:31.039 --> 00:10:32.200
taking three days off.

00:10:34.159 --> 00:10:36.559
The Heavens are really
playing a joke on me.

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:38.799
From now on, whatever I want to do,

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:40.799
I have to keep it from the Heavens.

00:10:40.799 --> 00:10:42.000
If they know, they'll ruin it.

00:10:42.559 --> 00:10:44.720
Who can keep things from them?

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:45.399
Me.

00:10:50.799 --> 00:10:51.679
Then have a candy.

00:10:55.559 --> 00:10:56.559
You took so many.

00:10:57.039 --> 00:10:58.200
Here, have some candy.

00:10:58.200 --> 00:10:59.480
- What?
- Wedding candy.

00:11:00.039 --> 00:11:00.799
Give me one.

00:11:00.799 --> 00:11:01.720
- Okay.
- Thanks.

00:11:02.200 --> 00:11:03.600
Take it. Here. Wedding candy.

00:11:03.679 --> 00:11:04.240
Thank you.

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:06.759
Wedding candy.

00:11:06.912 --> 00:11:08.320
We haven't got our certificate,

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:09.799
- Have some candy.
- and you're giving away the candy.

00:11:09.799 --> 00:11:11.039
Ma'am, wedding candy.

00:11:11.039 --> 00:11:12.919
I haven't had my wedding candy yet.

00:11:12.919 --> 00:11:14.120
Eat it. I'll peel one for you.

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.559
Come on, open your mouth. here.

00:11:20.759 --> 00:11:22.080
(Ningzhou Department Store)
Here, have some wedding candy.

00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:23.080
Have some wedding candy.

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.720
Let the child have some.

00:11:25.039 --> 00:11:26.879
Take my wedding candy. Here.

00:11:26.879 --> 00:11:27.759
Thank you.

00:11:27.919 --> 00:11:29.320
Child, take some wedding candy.

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:30.559
- He gave you candy. Say thank you.
- Here.

00:11:30.559 --> 00:11:31.159
Thank you.

00:11:31.159 --> 00:11:31.659
Take it.

00:11:31.659 --> 00:11:32.159
Thank you.

00:11:32.159 --> 00:11:32.659
Take it.

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:33.879
Look.

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:36.879
- Is it Hu Sanyuan?
- Is it?

00:11:36.879 --> 00:11:37.379
Hu Sanyuan!

00:11:39.159 --> 00:11:39.679
Dachui!

00:11:40.700 --> 00:11:41.200
What's up?

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:41.700
Dachui!

00:11:43.080 --> 00:11:43.919
Caixiang!

00:11:43.919 --> 00:11:44.799
What are you doing?

00:11:45.860 --> 00:11:46.360
What's this?

00:11:46.360 --> 00:11:46.919
Take it. Here.

00:11:46.919 --> 00:11:47.960
So you two are here.

00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:49.360
Wedding candy. What's wrong?

00:11:49.559 --> 00:11:50.159
You two's?

00:11:50.399 --> 00:11:51.279
- Wedding candy?
- Wedding candy.

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:53.679
Congrats! You've finally been together.

00:11:53.679 --> 00:11:55.639
You've finally been together.

00:11:55.639 --> 00:11:57.960
Good, congrats!
You should've done so long ago.

00:11:57.960 --> 00:11:59.080
What are you guys up to?

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:00.200
Going to perform opera.

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:01.472
I started an amateur troupe.

00:12:01.879 --> 00:12:04.559
Our amateur troupe
is very popular with the locals.

00:12:04.559 --> 00:12:05.320
Very popular.

00:12:05.320 --> 00:12:06.559
We perform all around the area.

00:12:06.559 --> 00:12:08.159
Right? Are you heading now to perform?

00:12:08.159 --> 00:12:09.000
Are you two coming?

00:12:09.399 --> 00:12:10.840
Come on. Let's go together!

00:12:10.840 --> 00:12:11.519
Let's go.

00:12:11.519 --> 00:12:12.360
Sing opera, okay?

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:13.039
Let's go.

00:12:13.399 --> 00:12:14.399
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

00:12:14.399 --> 00:12:15.559
Have some candy.

00:12:15.559 --> 00:12:16.559
Have some candy.

00:13:08.679 --> 00:13:11.360
(Yi Qin'e returns
to her familiar routine,)

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:14.759
(constantly practicing and rehearsing.)

00:13:15.080 --> 00:13:18.399
(She feels this is what it means
to live meaningfully.)

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:20.720
(Returning to the stage,)

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:23.559
(singing for herself,
singing for the audience,)

00:13:23.759 --> 00:13:25.360
(and singing for the Heavens.)

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:30.720
(Now, no matter what fate grants her,)

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:33.159
(she could handle it.)

00:13:43.264 --> 00:13:48.222
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:13:49.580 --> 00:13:54.077
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:13:56.306 --> 00:14:01.248
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:14:02.592 --> 00:14:07.662
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:14:09.216 --> 00:14:11.040
♪Only by swallowing the rumors♪

00:14:11.648 --> 00:14:14.232
♪Do you truly shine♪

00:14:15.616 --> 00:14:20.074
♪Who made the
raging flames so scorching♪

00:14:22.133 --> 00:14:24.544
♪Only by soaking in bitterness♪

00:14:24.544 --> 00:14:27.347
♪Is your life as tough as rock♪

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:34.240
♪After all,
your pure light stings like salt♪

00:14:38.240 --> 00:14:41.575
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:14:41.575 --> 00:14:44.768
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:14:44.768 --> 00:14:50.099
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:14:51.296 --> 00:14:54.528
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:14:55.136 --> 00:14:57.280
(Rhinestone accessories
kingfisher-feather headdress)

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:03.550
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:22.400
♪Only those who lead♪

00:15:22.784 --> 00:15:25.979
♪Take arrows from behind♪

00:15:26.944 --> 00:15:31.381
♪After all, your steps are so light♪

00:15:33.536 --> 00:15:35.456
♪Only a broken string♪

00:15:35.904 --> 00:15:39.110
♪Can echo through the sky♪

00:15:39.860 --> 00:15:46.214
♪After all,
only the echo shakes the roof♪

00:15:49.632 --> 00:15:52.960
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:56.276
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:15:56.309 --> 00:16:01.504
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:16:02.688 --> 00:16:05.856
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:16:05.856 --> 00:16:09.196
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:16:09.196 --> 00:16:14.859
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:16:44.608 --> 00:16:48.172
♪The moon is so high in the sky♪

00:16:48.931 --> 00:16:52.625
♪On a white horse over the stone bridge♪

00:16:53.289 --> 00:16:56.603
♪Curved bridge reflects the mountains♪

00:16:57.088 --> 00:17:01.536
♪Myriad lights share the reunion♪

00:17:02.144 --> 00:17:04.256
♪Yi Qin'e, you'll rise high♪

00:17:04.800 --> 00:17:06.336
♪Train with red silk; walk on stilts♪

00:17:06.336 --> 00:17:07.533
♪Stilts sway onstage♪

00:17:07.533 --> 00:17:14.048
♪Singing joys and sorrows to the skies♪

00:17:14.048 --> 00:17:17.356
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:17:17.356 --> 00:17:20.659
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:17:20.710 --> 00:17:26.641
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:17:26.736 --> 00:17:30.272
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:17:30.272 --> 00:17:33.587
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:17:33.587 --> 00:17:40.124
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:18:14.360 --> 00:18:16.440
Sorry I'm late.

00:18:18.159 --> 00:18:20.399
Ms. Han, why are you here?

00:18:21.559 --> 00:18:22.879
They'll be here any minute.

00:18:22.879 --> 00:18:24.000
I took a taxi by myself.

00:18:24.279 --> 00:18:27.440
Over two hundred yuan.
I wonder if Sissy Xue will reimburse me.

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:29.539
Don't worry about it. Don't.

00:18:29.840 --> 00:18:31.120
Hurry, take that off.

00:18:31.120 --> 00:18:33.960
For rehearsal, you can't wear that.

00:18:35.879 --> 00:18:36.519
Wear this.

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:54.759
Gorgeous!

00:20:20.359 --> 00:20:27.960
♪The sky is clear and bright♪

00:20:29.359 --> 00:20:32.480
♪My spirit is refreshed♪

00:21:03.480 --> 00:21:22.680
♪The garden
is filled with spring scenery♪

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:42.759
♪The willows♪

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:44.799
Come on, bring my costume over, hurry.

00:21:44.799 --> 00:21:45.400
Come on.

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:47.559
Hurry up, everyone, move it!

00:21:48.519 --> 00:21:49.079
Hurry!

00:21:51.319 --> 00:21:54.160
What was Qin'e thinking?
Didn't even tell us about the rehearsal.

00:21:54.759 --> 00:21:55.559
Enough chatter.

00:21:56.480 --> 00:21:57.279
Put on makeup now.

00:21:57.559 --> 00:21:58.359
Get ready.

00:22:04.359 --> 00:22:04.920
Good!

00:22:07.240 --> 00:22:08.119
Here, have water.

00:22:31.680 --> 00:22:41.440
♪A gust of fragrant wind♪

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:42.640
Sorry I'm late.

00:22:43.360 --> 00:22:58.715
♪Intoxicating♪

00:23:01.536 --> 00:23:16.039
♪Plum blossoms on the wall glow crimson♪

00:23:16.039 --> 00:23:16.559
Bro.

00:23:16.599 --> 00:23:17.119
What's up?

00:23:17.359 --> 00:23:18.759
I paid for this whole show.

00:23:18.759 --> 00:23:19.559
I'm sorry.

00:23:19.640 --> 00:23:21.160
You are blocking my view.

00:23:21.160 --> 00:23:21.960
I'm sorry.

00:23:21.960 --> 00:23:22.480
Move aside.

00:23:22.480 --> 00:23:23.000
Okay.

00:23:23.616 --> 00:23:25.714
♪Thief, thief♪

00:23:25.714 --> 00:23:27.976
♪I'm not a thief, not a thief♪

00:23:29.280 --> 00:23:30.624
♪Who are you?♪

00:23:31.840 --> 00:23:36.327
♪I am Pei Ruiqing,
a scholar of the Imperial Academy♪

00:23:38.240 --> 00:23:40.832
♪So it's Scholar Pei who has arrived♪

00:23:40.832 --> 00:23:44.935
♪Xiaying, help him up quickly♪

00:23:44.992 --> 00:23:46.400
♪Yes♪

00:23:46.440 --> 00:23:47.880
Is this how the eyebrows are drawn?

00:23:49.200 --> 00:23:49.720
Good.

00:23:49.740 --> 00:23:51.000
Right, they are drawn this way.

00:23:51.500 --> 00:23:52.000
Leave it.

00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:52.759
It's okay.

00:23:54.640 --> 00:23:55.880
Just like this.

00:23:56.240 --> 00:23:58.359
Twist this hair up and wrap it.

00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:07.720
The Lakeside Tour scene, get ready.

00:24:07.720 --> 00:24:09.000
Get on standby.

00:24:10.039 --> 00:24:11.759
Everyone, be on high alert!

00:24:12.119 --> 00:24:13.000
- Okay.
- Okay.

00:24:13.240 --> 00:24:14.176
Where is Liu Jinsong?

00:26:10.920 --> 00:26:11.480
- Good!
- Good!

00:27:58.279 --> 00:28:00.359
(What opera does my uncle
like to hear the most?)

00:28:01.799 --> 00:28:04.039
(Yang Men Nyu Jiang:
Exploring the Valley.)

00:28:06.720 --> 00:28:09.640
(Then have you sung it for him alone?)

00:28:10.279 --> 00:28:11.160
(No.)

00:28:15.200 --> 00:28:16.680
(Then do you want to sing for him?)

00:28:20.200 --> 00:28:21.000
Yes.

00:28:28.736 --> 00:28:37.871
♪The wind howls♪

00:28:39.040 --> 00:28:45.481
♪The mist is thick♪

00:29:43.440 --> 00:29:44.440
(When you turn around,)

00:29:46.720 --> 00:29:48.880
(I will be right behind you.)

00:30:11.168 --> 00:30:14.179
♪How did I fall for you♪

00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:18.241
♪I'm asking myself♪

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:22.361
♪I can give up anything♪

00:30:22.528 --> 00:30:26.070
♪Yet today I can't bear to leave♪

00:30:27.046 --> 00:30:30.276
♪You're not beautiful♪

00:30:30.656 --> 00:30:34.411
♪But you're utterly adorable♪

00:30:35.168 --> 00:30:38.158
♪Cinderella♪

00:30:39.104 --> 00:30:42.137
♪My Cinderella♪

00:30:44.576 --> 00:30:47.738
♪How did I fall for you♪

00:30:48.512 --> 00:30:51.456
♪I'm asking myself♪

00:30:52.096 --> 00:30:55.263
♪I can give up anything♪

00:30:55.712 --> 00:30:59.104
♪Yet today I can't bear to leave♪

00:31:00.128 --> 00:31:02.848
♪You're not beautiful♪

00:31:03.424 --> 00:31:06.961
♪But you're utterly adorable♪

00:31:07.808 --> 00:31:10.592
♪Cinderella♪

00:31:11.552 --> 00:31:14.483
♪My Cinderella♪

00:31:23.087 --> 00:31:25.920
♪I keep breaking your heart♪

00:31:26.784 --> 00:31:29.681
♪I'm always so cruel♪

00:31:30.592 --> 00:31:33.541
♪I tell you not to take it seriously♪

00:31:34.240 --> 00:31:37.696
♪Because I dare not believe it♪

00:31:38.560 --> 00:31:41.504
♪You are so beautiful♪

00:31:41.824 --> 00:31:45.479
♪And you're utterly adorable♪

00:31:46.208 --> 00:31:49.175
♪Cinderella♪

00:31:50.009 --> 00:31:53.029
♪My Cinderella♪

00:32:09.216 --> 00:32:12.139
♪Perhaps you never♪

00:32:12.578 --> 00:32:15.848
♪Thought that my heart would ache♪

00:32:16.735 --> 00:32:19.851
♪If this is a dream♪

00:32:20.361 --> 00:32:26.752
♪I'd rather stay drunk than wake♪

00:32:32.384 --> 00:32:35.705
♪I've endured♪

00:32:36.107 --> 00:32:39.365
♪I've waited♪

00:32:39.584 --> 00:32:43.432
♪Perhaps for your arrival♪

00:32:43.432 --> 00:32:47.362
♪Perhaps for your arrival♪

00:32:51.041 --> 00:32:55.443
♪Perhaps for your arrival♪

00:33:02.559 --> 00:33:05.759
(Hu Sanyuan finally
fulfills his promise.)

00:33:05.799 --> 00:33:08.839
(He takes Hua Caixiang with a tricycle)

00:33:08.880 --> 00:33:11.920
(to perform opera all around.)

00:33:12.519 --> 00:33:17.000
(Their opera troupe wanders
through the Qinling Mountains,)

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:21.160
(performing for several years.)

00:33:29.039 --> 00:33:33.200
(Travel Around Qinqiang Opera Troupe)
♪Only because the prince is so young♪

00:33:33.200 --> 00:33:37.359
(Qinqiang Opera Hei Ding Ben)
♪Let my father rule for a few years♪

00:33:37.359 --> 00:33:41.559
♪Open up the record of merit♪

00:33:41.559 --> 00:33:45.680
♪See what your father has done♪

00:33:45.680 --> 00:33:47.960
♪Sons who wrong their fathers die young♪

00:33:47.960 --> 00:33:50.200
♪Sons wronged by their fathers run away♪

00:33:50.200 --> 00:33:52.640
♪Brothers who wrong
each other bring discord♪

00:33:52.640 --> 00:33:54.640
♪Wronged brothers will part ways♪

00:33:54.640 --> 00:33:56.160
♪How can a wife oppress her husband♪

00:33:56.160 --> 00:33:57.559
♪A true man lives with dignity♪

00:33:57.559 --> 00:33:58.920
♪The emperor rules all♪

00:33:58.920 --> 00:34:00.200
♪Only the Xus are second to him♪

00:34:00.200 --> 00:34:01.480
♪The emperor rules all♪

00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:02.799
♪It's ruled half by his court♪

00:34:02.799 --> 00:34:03.920
♪This realm belongs to me♪

00:34:03.920 --> 00:34:05.240
♪No need to consult you♪

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:06.599
♪Your realm was built♪

00:34:06.599 --> 00:34:07.799
♪By our families♪

00:34:07.799 --> 00:34:09.119
♪Do you want the throne♪

00:34:09.119 --> 00:34:10.519
♪No, but I won't give it away♪

00:34:10.519 --> 00:34:11.680
♪I have to give it to him♪

00:34:11.680 --> 00:34:12.960
♪No, you truly can't♪

00:34:12.960 --> 00:34:14.200
♪You were given such a high post♪

00:34:14.200 --> 00:34:15.480
♪Now, you ignore me♪

00:34:15.480 --> 00:34:16.799
♪I earned my post♪

00:34:16.799 --> 00:34:18.000
♪Not your benevolence♪

00:34:18.000 --> 00:34:19.240
♪You should've been beheaded♪

00:34:19.240 --> 00:34:20.559
♪You can't behead me♪

00:34:20.559 --> 00:34:21.799
♪I must behead you♪

00:34:21.799 --> 00:34:23.079
♪No, you truly can't♪

00:34:23.079 --> 00:34:24.240
♪I'll have the guards♪

00:34:24.240 --> 00:34:26.640
♪Hang your head at the Meridian Gate♪

00:34:28.240 --> 00:34:29.759
- Good!
- Good!

00:34:37.880 --> 00:34:38.920
Whose kids are these?

00:34:38.920 --> 00:34:39.680
Have you eaten?

00:34:39.819 --> 00:34:40.319
Hurry.

00:34:40.319 --> 00:34:42.119
Look after them!

00:34:44.920 --> 00:34:47.039
What's wrong?
Why are you sitting down again?

00:34:48.319 --> 00:34:50.400
Sitting down here
to watch you perform on stage

00:34:51.200 --> 00:34:51.920
is more enjoyable.

00:34:57.119 --> 00:34:58.319
After all these years,

00:34:59.880 --> 00:35:02.559
He Dachui's drumming skills
haven't improved a bit.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:05.279
The skills haven't improved,
but the man has.

00:35:06.359 --> 00:35:08.000
He really loves opera.

00:35:09.279 --> 00:35:10.599
He doesn't look up when drumming,

00:35:11.119 --> 00:35:12.319
always keeping his head down.

00:35:12.880 --> 00:35:13.519
Sanyuan.

00:35:14.799 --> 00:35:15.960
Here, have a smoke.

00:35:16.799 --> 00:35:18.359
When have you ever seen me smoke?

00:35:20.119 --> 00:35:21.359
I have something to tell you.

00:35:24.079 --> 00:35:25.400
I'm leaving first.

00:35:26.839 --> 00:35:28.599
What's wrong? Did you get cancer?

00:35:28.880 --> 00:35:30.400
Can you even speak something nice?

00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:31.839
You said you were leaving first.

00:35:32.079 --> 00:35:34.039
My grandson is
in elementary school in Chang'an.

00:35:34.039 --> 00:35:36.759
Their parents are busy, so they asked me
to help take care of him.

00:35:36.759 --> 00:35:38.000
Why curse me having cancer?

00:35:41.079 --> 00:35:42.000
I understand.

00:35:42.759 --> 00:35:43.400
Just go.

00:35:47.519 --> 00:35:48.159
What?

00:35:48.639 --> 00:35:51.400
I thought you'd cry and beg me to stay.

00:35:54.360 --> 00:35:56.159
Then what about the troupe when I leave?

00:35:56.719 --> 00:35:59.280
We won't stop just because you are gone.

00:35:59.800 --> 00:36:00.679
You...

00:36:00.960 --> 00:36:04.519
Sanyuan, you've never taken me
seriously your whole life. Never!

00:36:05.360 --> 00:36:06.880
You laugh. You all just laugh.

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:08.559
I-I'm leaving. I'm leaving first.

00:36:12.280 --> 00:36:13.239
He's so angry.

00:36:17.679 --> 00:36:19.320
Liu Suona is leaving too.

00:36:21.159 --> 00:36:23.719
If this goes on,
there won't be many left.

00:36:25.079 --> 00:36:25.800
Just go ahead.

00:36:26.880 --> 00:36:28.440
The show can't go on without them?

00:36:30.719 --> 00:36:32.320
The two of us can go on a honeymoon.

00:36:34.960 --> 00:36:36.360
You always say I'm sentimental.

00:36:36.920 --> 00:36:39.280
Look at you,
even talking about a honeymoon.

00:36:47.760 --> 00:36:48.440
I'm leaving.

00:36:48.679 --> 00:36:49.199
Go.

00:36:53.760 --> 00:36:55.840
He, don't forget.

00:36:56.199 --> 00:36:57.280
Keep in touch.

00:37:06.360 --> 00:37:07.719
Then let's go too.

00:37:08.760 --> 00:37:09.440
Hold on a second.

00:37:18.400 --> 00:37:20.800
Hu Sanyuan!

00:37:21.599 --> 00:37:23.360
Wherever you go, let me know.

00:37:23.840 --> 00:37:25.360
Once I get the kid settled,

00:37:25.719 --> 00:37:27.119
I'll be back.

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:05.320
(The Protagonist by Qin Bawa)

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:06.960
(What is a protagonist?)

00:38:07.719 --> 00:38:11.039
(Yi Qin'e finally understands.)

00:38:11.440 --> 00:38:13.888
(It's not just the one standing
in the center of the stage)

00:38:13.888 --> 00:38:15.392
(who is the protagonist.)

00:38:16.480 --> 00:38:18.960
(Everyone who toughs it out in life)

00:38:18.960 --> 00:38:21.719
(and hasn't fallen, is one.)

00:38:23.000 --> 00:38:24.519
(In one's life,)

00:38:24.639 --> 00:38:27.000
(others can help set the stage,)

00:38:27.280 --> 00:38:32.000
(but one has to perform until the end.)

00:38:32.000 --> 00:38:34.840
Keep going.
After this slope, we'll arrive.

00:38:35.460 --> 00:38:35.960
Alright.

00:38:35.960 --> 00:38:36.460
Go.

00:38:40.079 --> 00:38:40.679
Go.

00:38:42.599 --> 00:38:44.800
Next time we should
bring an extra battery.

00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:47.440
One battery won't last this long.

00:38:48.519 --> 00:38:50.000
One isn't even enough.

00:38:51.039 --> 00:38:52.239
I'm tired. Let's take a rest.

00:38:58.519 --> 00:39:00.199
Why is it snowing now?

00:39:01.119 --> 00:39:02.639
After the show, we couldn't get down.

00:39:04.440 --> 00:39:06.239
If we can't get down, just stay up here.

00:39:07.119 --> 00:39:08.519
Let's perform nonstop.

00:39:09.000 --> 00:39:10.840
Let's perform for even half a month.

00:39:13.360 --> 00:39:14.239
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

00:39:14.920 --> 00:39:15.480
Go.

00:39:15.480 --> 00:39:16.159
Come on.

00:39:21.480 --> 00:39:22.119
Push harder.

00:39:35.079 --> 00:39:35.920
Why is there no one?

00:39:41.480 --> 00:39:44.079
Sir, is Zhou Eryong here?

00:39:44.519 --> 00:39:45.159
Who is it?

00:39:45.440 --> 00:39:48.280
Zhou Eryong!
He asked us to come perform.

00:39:48.840 --> 00:39:50.960
Zhou Eryong?
There is no such person here.

00:39:52.400 --> 00:39:53.719
There's no such person here!

00:39:56.280 --> 00:39:57.280
There is no such person.

00:39:58.880 --> 00:39:59.880
We've been tricked.

00:40:00.239 --> 00:40:01.039
Tricked?

00:40:06.320 --> 00:40:06.820
Don't worry.

00:40:07.280 --> 00:40:08.480
The stage is here.

00:40:08.719 --> 00:40:10.199
No one can trick us out of it.

00:40:10.800 --> 00:40:11.320
Exactly.

00:40:13.320 --> 00:40:14.144
Unload the stuff.

00:40:26.639 --> 00:40:27.920
What are you selling?

00:40:28.119 --> 00:40:29.280
We're not selling anything.

00:40:30.039 --> 00:40:31.880
We perform opera, kid.

00:40:31.880 --> 00:40:32.800
Goudan!

00:40:33.559 --> 00:40:34.840
What are they selling?

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:36.719
Perform opera for money!

00:40:38.519 --> 00:40:40.000
What did you say?

00:40:40.679 --> 00:40:42.519
We need no money. We just perform opera.

00:40:42.519 --> 00:40:44.159
Old man, why are you cursing me?

00:40:44.159 --> 00:40:45.079
You little brat,

00:40:45.639 --> 00:40:46.559
talking nonsense!

00:40:47.880 --> 00:40:48.380
Go!

00:40:49.039 --> 00:40:49.880
Go home

00:40:50.360 --> 00:40:53.480
and tell your family
to come here to enjoy the opera.

00:40:53.519 --> 00:40:54.800
I bet you can't sing a note!

00:40:55.039 --> 00:40:56.199
You can't sing!

00:40:57.639 --> 00:40:58.719
You little brats!

00:41:00.039 --> 00:41:00.639
Come on.

00:41:01.400 --> 00:41:02.679
Let's sing a note.

00:41:04.519 --> 00:41:07.760
♪On this day last year,
inside this gate♪

00:41:08.199 --> 00:41:12.440
♪Her face blushed like peach blossoms♪

00:41:36.224 --> 00:41:41.305
(Sun and moon connects bamboos)

00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:44.960
(The opera ends)

00:42:45.800 --> 00:42:47.199
(and audience disperses,)

00:42:48.679 --> 00:42:51.559
(but Qinqiang opera remains.)

00:42:53.039 --> 00:42:54.440
(For thousands of years,)

00:42:55.000 --> 00:42:57.760
(it's still been lively.)

00:43:00.480 --> 00:43:04.544
(The end)

00:43:05.000 --> 00:43:09.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:11.090 --> 00:43:15.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:17.370 --> 00:43:21.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:23.120 --> 00:43:30.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:43:44.790 --> 00:43:48.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:43:50.140 --> 00:43:55.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:43:56.830 --> 00:44:00.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:02.020 --> 00:44:07.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:08.770 --> 00:44:12.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:14.010 --> 00:44:19.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:20.810 --> 00:44:25.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:26.180 --> 00:44:31.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:44:32.020 --> 00:44:37.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:44:38.080 --> 00:44:43.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:44:43.890 --> 00:44:49.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:44:50.120 --> 00:44:55.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:44:55.930 --> 00:45:01.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:01.900 --> 00:45:07.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:07.960 --> 00:45:12.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:13.940 --> 00:45:19.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:20.020 --> 00:45:29.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪